The paper deals with the construction of MDS array codes, which are commonly studied in the information theory (cs.IT) and distributed systems (cs.DS) communities. The concept of optimal access is also relevant to the field of storage systems (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the repair problem, which is a common topic in networked information systems (cs.NI) and coding theory (cs.CC).
